Package com.orange.api.rfid.capture.application.server.configure

Orange RFID System - EPC application [Module epcis_application-server] Configuration WS implementations
Mainly include ConfigureImpl for setting/getting parameters, vocabularies (VocabularyType) and business process events (BPEventType), as well as ConfigurePsionImpl for simpler functions for mobile readers

Class Summary
ConfigureHttpServlet Servlet implementation class ConfigureHttpServlet Includes post, get and delete functions from @see ConfigureManager as HTTP requests
ConfigureImpl  
ConfigureManager This class is called by ConfigureImpl web methods to manage reading, writing and deleting of single: BusinessProcessEvent CaptureEvent QueryEvent GPIOEvent SubscriberEvent VocabularyObject BusinessProcessObject It also manages post, get and delete actions for VocabularyElementType and BPEventElementType.
ConfigurePsionImpl  
ConfigureUploadGui This class is a GUI to upload VocabularyType and BPEventType XML files.
 

Package com.orange.api.rfid.capture.application.server.configure Description

Orange RFID System - EPC application [Module epcis_application-server]

Configuration WS implementations
Mainly include ConfigureImpl for setting/getting parameters, vocabularies (VocabularyType) and business process events (BPEventType), as well as ConfigurePsionImpl for simpler functions for mobile readers
